          "text": "All permitted uses in the WF Zone are subject to the following regulations: Minimum: 10 m (32.3 ft) Maximum: 16.5 m (54.1 ft) properties adjacent to Water St Maximum: 24.5 m (80.4 ft) for all other properties.",
